        <name>det_threshold_power</name>
        <param>
          <type>double</type>
          <declname>pfa</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Power threshold p from Pfa for the power detector. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Exact closed-form: P(Exponential(1) &gt; p) = exp(-p) = Pfa, so</para>
<para>p = -ln(Pfa)</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>pfa</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Desired false-alarm probability; must be in (0, 1). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Threshold p &gt; 0.</para>
</simplesect>
Example: det_threshold_power(1e-6) = 6·ln(10) ~ 13.816 </para>
        </detaileddescription>
